Title: Graph images: use a consistent position for the graph time range
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: reporting
Date: 1632312693
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.0.0p12

In reports the graph time range is now diplayed on the top right. Before
it was added directly after the title. In HTML emails of notifications
and PNG exports a small margin on the right is added.
